{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    { "type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "9.0.0" },
    { "type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "1.0.0" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "stat", "name": "Stat", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "timeseries", "name": "Time series", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "table", "name": "Table", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "state-timeline", "name": "State timeline", "version": "" }
  ],
  "id": null,
  "uid": "tunnel-selfheal",
  "title": "Tunnel Self-Healing Monitor",
  "description": "Monitoramento e auto-recupera√ß√£o dos t√∫neis do homelab (cloudflared, SSH, nginx, Docker)",
  "tags": ["tunnels", "self-healing", "homelab", "cloudflared", "infrastructure"],
  "style": "dark",
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "liveNow": false,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["5s", "10s", "30s", "1m", "5m"]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": { "selected": false, "text": "Prometheus", "value": "Prometheus" },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Datasource",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": { "selected": true, "text": "All", "value": "$__all" },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
        "definition": "label_values(tunnel_up, name)",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "label": "Tunnel",
        "multi": true,
        "name": "tunnel",
        "query": { "query": "label_values(tunnel_up, name)", "refId": "StandardVariableQuery" },
        "refresh": 2,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "sort": 1,
        "type": "query"
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "üü¢ Tunnel Status Overview",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_up{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} ({{type}})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            { "options": { "0": { "color": "red", "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "color": "green", "text": "UP" } }, "type": "value" }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "üìä Tunnel Health Timeline",
      "type": "state-timeline",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_up{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            { "options": { "0": { "color": "red", "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "color": "green", "text": "UP" } }, "type": "value" }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "alignValue": "left",
        "mergeValues": true,
        "rowHeight": 0.8,
        "showValue": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "‚è±Ô∏è Response Time (ms)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_response_time_seconds{name=~\"$tunnel\"} * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "axisSoftMin": 0
          },
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "üîÑ Self-Heal Restarts",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(tunnel_restart_total{name=~\"$tunnel\"}[5m]) * 300",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} restarts/5m",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_restart_total{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} total",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "stacking": { "mode": "none" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["sum", "lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "üö® Consecutive Failures",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_consecutive_failures{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "axisSoftMin": 0
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 3 }
            ]
          },
          "custom.thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "area" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "üìã Current Status Table",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_up{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_response_time_seconds{name=~\"$tunnel\"} * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "B",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_restart_total{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "C",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "expr": "tunnel_consecutive_failures{name=~\"$tunnel\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "D",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "name": "Tunnel",
              "type": "Type",
              "Value #A": "Status",
              "Value #B": "Latency (ms)",
              "Value #C": "Restarts",
              "Value #D": "Failures"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Status" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  { "options": { "0": { "color": "red", "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "color": "green", "text": "UP" } }, "type": "value" }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": { "type": "color-background" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Latency (ms)" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "ms" },
              { "id": "decimals", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": { "showHeader": true, "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Tunnel", "desc": false }] }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "‚ÑπÔ∏è Info",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Tunnel Self-Healing Monitor\n\n**Auto-recovery:** O sistema verifica a sa√∫de dos t√∫neis a cada 30s. Ap√≥s 2 falhas consecutivas, reinicia o servi√ßo automaticamente (m√°x. 3 restarts/hora).\n\n**T√∫neis monitorados:**\n- **cloudflared-rpa4all** ‚Äî Cloudflare Tunnel (dns/www/openwebui/grafana.rpa4all.com)\n- **nginx-proxy** ‚Äî Nginx reverse proxy (porta 8090)\n- **openwebui-docker** ‚Äî OpenWebUI container (porta 3000)\n- **grafana** ‚Äî Grafana container (porta 3002)\n- **dns-doh-proxy** ‚Äî DNS over HTTPS proxy (porta 8453)\n\n**Endpoints:** Prometheus `:9110/metrics` | Status `:9111/status` | Audit `:9111/audit`"
      }
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "icon": "external link",
      "tags": [],
      "title": "Tunnel Status API",
      "tooltip": "Live JSON status",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "http://192.168.15.2:9111/status"
    },
    {
      "icon": "doc",
      "tags": [],
      "title": "Audit Log",
      "tooltip": "Self-healing action log",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "http://192.168.15.2:9111/audit"
    }
  ]
}
